     VISN1 Home                     VA Worcester CBOC

   Photo of Worcester clinic VA Worcester CBOC
                                         605 Lincoln Street
                                         Worcester, MA 01605
                                        Phone: (508) 856-0104
                                         Fax: (508) 856-7425

                                           Practice Hours:
                                      8:00am - 4:30pm, Mon-Fri

                               Directions

       The Worcester clinic was established after the end of World War II in
     1946 as one of 18 VA field offices in Massachusetts. The Worcester
   Clinic has been located at its new site since May 18, 1993. This state
      of the art facility offers primary care with expanded programs in
   optometry, mental health, and rehabilitation medicine. In addition the
    clinic provides care in dermatology, geriatrics, podiatry and women's
       health. Radiology, pharmacy and laboratory support services are
   conveniently located on site. The clinic offers ample free parking and
    is accessible via public transportation. Shuttle service is available
               between the clinic and the West Roxbury Campus.

                                 DIRECTIONS:

   From Route 495: Take Exit 25B onto Route 290 West. Continue to Exit 20
    marked "Lincoln Street" heading north on Route 70. Clinic will be 0.8
                             miles on the right.

      From Route 290 heading West: Take Exit 20 marked "Lincoln Street"
      heading north on Route 70. Clinic will be 0.8 miles on the right.

    From Route 290 heading East: Take Exit 21 marked "Plantation Street".
   Take a left at the bottom of the exit ramp heading north on Plantation
     Street. At the 1st set of lights, take a left onto Lincoln Street.
                    Clinic will be 0.3 miles on the left.

   From Route 9: Take Plantation Street heading north (near UMass Medical
    Center). Continue 0.7 miles to the 1st set of traffic lights. Take a
   left at the lights onto Lincoln Street. Clinic will be 0.3 miles on the
                                    left.
